id: pm-1h99
title: "pm update-many --ids: explicit ID-list filter for targeted bulk mutations"
description: update-many accepts only filter predicates; an agent with a resolved ID set must re-express it as fragile filters or loop pm update. --ids gives a safe explicit allowlist composable with search --json | jq.
